### ==============================
### Configuration Management
### ==============================

### Get Manageable Configuration Properties
GET {{baseUrl}}/config/manageable
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json


### Update Manageable Configuration Property
PUT {{baseUrl}}/config/manageable
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "{{configKey}}",
  "value": "{{configValue}}" 
  // Set value to null to reset to default: "value": null
}


### Update Runtime Configuration Property (Legacy)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/config/runtime
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "key": "some.runtime.property",
  "value": "new_runtime_value"
}


### ==============================
### User Management
### ==============================

### Create a New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/users?username={{newUsername}}&email={{newUserEmail}}&password={{newUserPassword}}&roles={{newUserRoles}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### Get All Users
GET {{baseUrl}}/users
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json


### Update User
# Requires a valid userIdToManage
PUT {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userIdToManage}}?username={{newUsername}}_updated&email=updated_{{newUserEmail}}&roles=THEMATICIAN
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### Reset User Password
# Requires a valid userIdToManage
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userIdToManage}}/reset-password?newPassword=resetPassword789
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### Lock User Account
# Requires a valid userIdToManage
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userIdToManage}}/true 
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### Unlock User Account
# Requires a valid userIdToManage
POST {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userIdToManage}}/false
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### Delete User
# Requires a valid userIdToManage
# Be careful using this!
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/users/{{userIdToManage}}
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### ==============================
### Admin Signup Request Management
### ==============================

### Get Pending Admin Signup Requests
GET {{baseUrl}}/signup-requests/pending
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
Accept: application/json


### Approve Admin Signup Request
# Requires a valid signupRequestId for a PENDING request
POST {{baseUrl}}/signup-requests/{{signupRequestId}}/approve
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}


### Reject Admin Signup Request
# Requires a valid signupRequestId for a PENDING request
POST {{baseUrl}}/signup-requests/{{signupRequestId}}/reject
Authorization: Bearer {{adminToken}}
